Class Summary
Controller Provides the functionality to the Wileven Machine's components by sending and receiving information between the view and the interpreter, loader, and model.
InputInstructions To put the input information into the data structures that represent the memory and registers of the machine.
instructionCases This class will have static methods for executing all the instructions.
instructionParser This class will parse through the given Instructions.
InstructionTest  
Interpreter This class interprets the given instruction and executes it.
interpreterUtility This utility class provides methods that can be used for commonly performed operations in the Interpreter class.
MachineMain The main method for the Wileven Machine that creates instances of a model, view, and controller.
Model Use this class to store all the memory and register info in one spot since the loader, interpreter, and simulator all need access to it.
Utility A class that contains utility methods that all the other classes can use.
View Contains the GUI for the Wileven Machine.
